::Darkwing/Havotron::
Darkwing sends a comm to Havotron.
'They are going somewhere more private master, waht should i do?'

"Follow them...."

"Here we are Spinister" he then says turning to Spinister. "Now I 
want to talk about the team we have together. I want you to be second 
in command. You have what i was looking for in the other pathetic 
bots we have. All i can say to you tho, is no your place."
